column5: Got out in the wind and snow yesterday to do some perching. Didn't bring the hut cuz it was calm when we went out. Big mistake. Couldn't see too far in front as the winds picked up. As usual, the bite turned on for the bad weather. I always find the fish to turn on as a front rolls through. Yesterday was no exception.   Sorry for the late report, but the Mrs had me busy for the evening playing euchre.
N-I-C-E Perch!  - is that what you kids call it these days - "euchre"?    Tracker (Don)
He is "euchred " if he answer that too  Nice fish btw.

Eeeeeeewww!!!! Bad images of little old grannies at the seniors centre getting Bawdy The things this website is doing to my mind lately with "well dressed guys", "stick close to me and you'll get some", etc....
welease woger!! always look on the bright side of life..  ... uh oh
Nicely done Bruce and Rob Thanks for sharing Jacques
